headline: UBS Reassesses Rollins (ROL) Ahead of Earnings, Maintains Neutral View
summary: Rollins, Inc. (NYSE:ROL) is included among the 13 Best February Dividend Stocks to Buy. On January 21, UBS lifted its price target on Rollins, Inc. (NYSE:ROL) to $65 from $61 while keeping a Neutral rating on the stock. The firm said the setup heading into fourth-quarter results looks fairly balanced. Organic growth and EBITDA are […]
